Do you have a rigid board in your bed instead of a box?
Never!
Maximum for one guest bed for one night only.
However, equip the board (if there are no) with ventilation holes and use the spring mattress with a minimum height of 15cm with bag springs (from Taschenfederken Germany) and an aeration layer.
